sequenceDiagram
  participant U as 用户 User
  participant R as 运行时 Runtime
  participant S as 会话存储 SessionStore
  participant G as 网关 Gateway
  participant O as 编排器 Orchestrator
  participant SA as 路由代理 RouteAgent
  participant DA as 下游代理 DownstreamAgent
  participant T as 工具 Tool

  U->>R: 业务消息\nBusiness Message
  R->>S: 记录消息\nrecordBusinessMessage
  R->>G: 处理快照\nhandle(snapshot)
  G->>O: 路由输入 + 角色输入\nroute + role inputs
  O->>SA: 路由判定\nroute decision
  SA-->>O: 路由/意图/置信度\nroute + intent + confidence
  O->>DA: 执行单一路径\nrun downstream agent
  DA->>T: 工具动作\ntool action
  T-->>DA: 工具结果\ntool result
  DA-->>O: 最终计划/回复\nfinal plan/reply
  O-->>G: 下游结果\ndownstream result
  G->>S: 追加回复/更新工单\nappend reply / update state
  S-->>R: 会话快照回传\nsession snapshot updated
  R-->>U: 最终回复 + 跟踪\nfinal reply + trace
